---
title: "Non-contact Displacement Estimation Using Doppler Radar"
collection: talks
type: "Talk"
permalink: /talks/2012-08-28-talk-1
venue: "IEEE International Conference of the EMBS (EMBC)"
date: 2012-08-28
location: "San Diego, California"
---

In this paper we demonstrate that if relatively large motion is used to calibrate the radar system, smaller motion displacement may be acquired non-contactly with the accuracy on the order of 30 Î¼m.
